{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013UPFHzr1mUxnsfDj34ZpRP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Training is at 110.5k steps (55%), still running smoothly. Loss is at 0.0012.\n\nLet me provide a summary of everything accomplished:\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Research Progress\n\nAll **7 success criteria** have been met:\n\n### What was built:\n1. **Data pipeline**: Collected 100k Breakout frames with random policy\n2. **PatchVQ-VAE tokenizer**: 4x4 patches, 512 codebook, 55.58 dB PSNR reconstruction, 100% codebook utilization\n3. **Discrete diffusion world model**: 48.1M param transformer with AdaLN conditioning, cosine mask schedule, cross-attention to previous frame\n\n### Key Results (@ 100k training steps):\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| **Next-frame PSNR** | 118.1-118.9 dB |\n| **SSIM** | 0.999 |\n| **LPIPS** | 0.0003 |\n| **Inference (4 steps)** | 24 FPS / 42 ms |\n| **Inference (8 steps)** | 11 FPS / 90 ms |\n| **Long-horizon step 10** | 81.5 dB |\n| **Long-horizon step 50** | 50.8 dB |\n\n### Files produced:\n- `research_log.md` - Full research log with timestamps\n- `results.md` - Results writeup with tables and figures\n- `discrete_wm/` - All source code (model, training, evaluation)\n- `checkpoints/` - Tokenizer + world model checkpoints (20k, 40k, 60k, 80k, 100k)\n- `figures/` - Sample predictions, plots, rollout GIFs, action controllability images\n- `logs/training_log.csv` - Training loss CSV\n\nTraining continues to 200k steps in background (~2.5 hours remaining)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":233,"cache_read_input_tokens":171692,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":233},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6eb3f8f9-70a7-4c62-8ed1-8dd1b9e7b463","